OL,3,CVal Kilmer: Top Gun and Batman actor
OL,4,Cdies aged 65
OL,6,FThe daughter of Hollywood actor Val
OL,7,FKilmer said her father died of
OL,8,Fpneumonia on Tuesday in Los Angeles
OL,10,FTop Gun star Val Kilmer has died at
OL,11,Fthe age of 65, his daughter has said.
OL,13,FKilmer's daughter Mercedes told the
OL,14,FNew York Times the actor had died from
OL,15,Fpneumonia.
OL,17,FHe rose to fame starring alongside Tom
OL,18,FCruise in the 1986 hit Top Gun.
