OL,6,FKilmer would go on to play Batman in
OL,7,F1995's Batman Forever and received
OL,8,Fcritical acclaim for his portrayal of
OL,9,Fmusician Jim Morrison in the 1991 film
OL,10,FThe Doors.
OL,12,FKilmer's final acting role was a cameo
OL,13,Fin the 2022 blockbuster sequel Top
OL,14,FGun: Maverick.
OL,16,F"I just want to say that was pretty
OL,17,Femotional," Tom Cruise told Jimmy
OL,18,FKimmel in 2023 about the cameo.
