OL,3,CVal Kilmer: Top Gun and Batman actor
OL,4,Cdies aged 65
OL,6,F"I've known Val for decades, and for
OL,7,Fhim to come back and play that
OL,8,Fcharacter... he's such a powerful
OL,9,Factor that he instantly became that
OL,10,Fcharacter again."
OL,12,FHe underwent both radiotherapy and
OL,13,Fchemotherapy, as well as a
OL,14,Ftracheostomy, which damaged his vocal
OL,15,Fcords.
OL,17,F"I obviously am sounding much worse
OL,18,Fthan I feel," Kilmer said in the
OL,19,Fdocumentary.
