OL,3,CVal Kilmer: Top Gun and Batman actor
OL,4,Cdies aged 65
OL,6,F"I can't speak without plugging this
OL,7,Fhole (in his throat). You have to make
OL,8,Fthe choice to breathe or to eat.
OL,10,F"It's an obstacle that is very present
OL,11,Fwith whoever sees me."
OL,13,FIn a post on Instagram, actor Josh Gad
OL,14,Fpaid tribute to the action star.
OL,16,FHe said: "RIP Val Kilmer. Thank you
OL,17,Ffor defining so many of the movies of
OL,18,Fmy childhood. You truly were an icon."
