OL,6,FActor Josh Brolin, son of James
OL,7,FBrolin, said he was going to miss his
OL,8,F"pal".
OL,10,F"You were a smart, challenging, brave,
OL,11,Fuber-creative firecracker," he said in
OL,12,Fan Instagram post.
OL,14,F"There's not a lot left of those. I
OL,15,Fhope to see you up there in the
OL,16,Fheavens when I eventually get there.
OL,17,FUntil then, amazing memories, lovely
OL,18,Fthoughts."
